<div class="mm">
NPC: <span class="white">Ifirn</span><br />
Long Desc: <span class="white">Ifirn is deeply engrossed in study as you enter.</span><br />
<br /><span class="white">Firun is a small stout gnome.  She has bright rosy cheeks and a cheer<br />
disposition.  Dressed in flowing black robes, she sits on the floor of her<br />
room deeply engrossed in books of the ages.  Her flaxen hair glistens when<br />
the light touches it.  A wizard well versed in cleric spells and training,<br />
many people come from miles around to seek her guidance.  She greets you<br />
with a firm but friendly smile as you enter her shop.</span><br />
<span class="white">She is a gnome approximately 4'1" tall.</span><br />
<br/>
This NPC can be found in: <span class="white"><a href="/area/35">Lowangen</a></span>.<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&hellip;in <a href="/room/2300">Ifirn's Spell Study</a>.<br/><span class="yellow">*</span>This NPC is a shopkeeper.<br /><span class="yellow">*</span>This NPC is stationary.<br />This NPC is known to carry the following items:<br /><span style="white-space: pre;"> 1) <a href="/item/1293">a soggy, yellow-green scroll                                    </a> <span class="yellow">  5        3,125</span> gp<br /> 2) <a href="/item/1212">an amber scroll made of cowhide                                 </a> <span class="yellow"> 13        5,325</span> gp<br /> 3) <a href="/item/220">a midnight-blue scroll                                          </a> <span class="yellow"> 15        1,875</span> gp<br /> 4) <a href="/item/1294">an ebony colored icy scroll                                     </a> <span class="yellow"> 23          575</span> gp<br /> 5) <a href="/item/1295">a soggy cobalt scroll                                           </a> <span class="yellow"> 30          750</span> gp<br /> 6) <a href="/item/1296">an indigo scroll                                                </a> <span class="yellow"> 10          250</span> gp<br /> 7) <a href="/item/1297">a glazed crystal scroll                                         </a> <span class="yellow"> 40        1,500</span> gp<br /> 8) <a href="/item/221">an off-white scroll                                             </a> <span class="yellow"> 15          500</span> gp<br /> 9) <a href="/item/1298">a silvery rawhide scroll                                        </a> <span class="yellow">  5          650</span> gp<br />10) <a href="/item/356">a copper-colored scroll                                         </a> <span class="yellow">  5          450</span> gp<br />11) <a href="/item/1299">a rose-colored cotton scroll                                    </a> <span class="yellow"> 25        3,625</span> gp<br />12) <a href="/item/987">a platinum-colored scroll                                       </a> <span class="yellow"> 35        2,375</span> gp<br />13) <a href="/item/226">a navy blue scroll                                              </a> <span class="yellow">  5        1,625</span> gp<br />14) <a href="/item/1300">a lightning blue scroll                                         </a> <span class="yellow">  5        3,125</span> gp<br />15) <a href="/item/355">a didactic scroll                                               </a> <span class="yellow">  1          150</span> gp<br />16) <a href="/item/360">a spellbook bound in red leather                                </a> <span class="yellow"> 15        2,000</span> gp<br />17) <a href="/item/219">a spellbook bound in white leather                              </a> <span class="yellow">  1        1,000</span> gp<br />18) <a href="/item/363">a scroll crafted of annelid skin                                </a> <span class="yellow"> 25          735</span> gp<br /></span>This mob is required by the following quests:<br/>- <a href="/quest/3484">Clerical Discipline</a> (40-250) from <a href="/npc/3437">Lady Undya</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3525">Shamanic Debuffs</a> (40-250) from <a href="/npc/3437">Lady Undya</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3662">The Cleansing Paladin</a> (35-250) from <a href="/npc/388">Lord Telleri</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3746">Wizard Offensive Spells</a> (35-250) from <a href="/npc/255">Lord Vendredi</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3566">Leeching Lifeforce</a> (35-250) from <a href="/npc/3437">Lady Undya</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3664">Monk Curation</a> (30-250) from <a href="/npc/255">Lord Vendredi</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3669">Monks and Magical Items</a> (59-250) from <a href="/npc/255">Lord Vendredi</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3529">Clerical Curation</a> (35-250) from <a href="/npc/3437">Lady Undya</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3719">Mental Magical Defense</a> (55-250) from <a href="/npc/255">Lord Vendredi</a>.<br/>- <a href="/quest/3660">A Monk's Magical Manipulation</a> (50-250) from <a href="/npc/255">Lord Vendre